divs: Sighting DetailsA woman walking near her home observed a cylindrical object nearly overhead atan estimated 30,000 feet altitude. The object appeared faster and larger than ajetliner, had tapered rounded ends, and either glowed white or reflectedsunlight. No contrail was observed. It was lost from view in the distance in8-10 seconds when it appeared to "blink out".
